<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hun a tawm tai lei nawpna cheng le a bei zel,
 Khawvel ah kipahna kim thei ngeilo;
 Lalpa hung leng inla nilopi hun tun in,
 Gimthei chate'n lei dahum pawtsan a nuom tau.

[V2]
 Aw, Eden thak nuom a chun ei pui kai in,
 Lungngai taka khensate zalaia buol di'n
 Kipahna kim tan tin hun pak zel ungkau
 Khawvel hi ngaikit ta puong kau, Na gam achun.

[V3]
 2. Nang dinga thuoksa te'n gam nuom tun kinem ui,
 Lei nawpna a mau di'n pak bang a tuoi;
 Zion mipite leh hehpihna Lal mel chu,
 Ni lopi hung tung ding chuh a thil chim ngei puou.

[V4]
 3. Lei lungngaih leh gimtheih buoina tin cheng nuoiah,
 Nang hun gingten kipak in la a sau;
 Amau di'n khuo vak hen Salem thak nuom a chun,
 Na puih khawm phat ni lopi ngaiin a thil ui.</lyrics>
<title>Aw Eden Thak</title>
<author>Puna</author>
<hymn_number>203</hymn_number>
</song>